WEBVTT



00:00:35.296 --> 00:00:39.936
Hi everyone and welcome to Central. We are thrilled that you have chosen to worship with us today.

00:00:41.504 --> 00:00:51.552
We are one church in multiple locations, and we are here to reach those we have not yet reached and lead them into a growing relationship with Jesus Christ. It's as simple as reach, connect,

00:00:51.072 --> 00:00:53.536
Connect disciple sin

00:00:56.384 --> 00:01:06.432
If you have any other questions, you can go to our website or download the CBC app, where you can get more information about our church and its ministries. Find out about the latest events, plus watch past semester.

00:01:05.952 --> 00:01:13.504
past messages. And please follow our campuses and ministries on social media. They are easy to find on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter.

00:01:13.696 --> 00:01:18.400
Again, thank you so much for joining us. We're truly glad you're here.
